author: Dominic King For Mailonline
title: Liverpool FC news: Jordan Henderson to miss Leicester tie | Daily Mail Online
text: Liverpool captain Jordan Henderson to miss Leicester clash with foot injury Jordan Henderson out of Liverpool's trip to Leicester on Monday night Henderson has not travelled to the East Midlands because of a badly bruised foot Liverpool had hoped he would recover from the knock picked up in training There is no suggestion that Henderson has suffered any bone damage But he could also be out of match against Arsenal on Saturday
